<%- include('partials/header') %>

<!,  Custom bespoke styles for the About Us page , >
<style>
  .about-hero-banner {
    position: relative;
    padding: 10rem 2rem 8rem;
    background-image: url('https://res.cloudinary.com/dawp1fcci/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1784235734/pexels-axp-photography-500641970-19227962_dxtxnr.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .about-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .about-hero-container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .about-hero-banner h1 {
    font-family: var(, font-serif);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .about-hero-banner p {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(, color-accent-terracotta);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .about-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about-grid.reverse {
    direction: rtl;
  }
  .about-grid.reverse .about-text-block {
    direction: ltr;
  }
  .about-text-block h2 {
    font-family: var(, font-serif);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(, color-primary);
  }
  .about-text-block p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #444444;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .about-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(, border-radius-large);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(, box-shadow-medium);
  }
  .about-image-wrapper img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 480px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: var(, transition-smooth);
  }
  .about-image-wrapper img:hover {
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  /* Split Highlight Section */
  .crisis-bg-section {
    background-color: var(, color-bg-warm-gray);
    border-top: 1px solid var(, color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(, color-border);
  }

  /* Culinary Craft Gallery */
  .craft-showcase-section {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .craft-showcase-section h2 {
    font-family: var(, font-serif);
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .craft-intro-text {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #555555;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .craft-collage-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .collage-card {
    border-radius: var(, border-radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(, box-shadow-soft);
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid var(, color-border);
  }
  .collage-card img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 250px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .collage-card-body {
    padding: 1.2rem;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .collage-card-body h4 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: var(, color-primary);
  }
  .collage-card-body p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #666666;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Bottom Collage Section */
  .brand-gallery-section {
    background-color: #050505;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .brand-gallery-section h2 {
    font-family: var(, font-serif);
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .brand-gallery-section p {
    color: #cccccc;
  }
  .gallery-split-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .gallery-img-col img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 380px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(, border-radius);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    .about-hero-banner h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    .craft-collage-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
    .gallery-split-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<!,  About Hero , >
<section class="about-hero-banner">
  <div class="about-hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="about-hero-container">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>Taste You Can Trust</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!,  Section 1: The Modern Food Crisis , >
<section class="about-section crisis-bg-section">
  <div class="container about-grid">
    <div class="about-text-block">
      <h2>The Crisis on Our Tables</h2>
      <p>
        In today's fast-paced world, convenience has hijacked the dining table. Generation after generation is growing up relying heavily on highly processed junk foods, pre-packaged meals, and chemical-laden fast food options. 
      </p>
      <p>
        This shift in food intake is having a quiet but devastating effect on our bodies. It robs us of our natural strength, vitality, and physical stamina, leading to early illnesses and long-term health issues. When our daily food is stripped of its nutritional value and replaced with synthetic preservatives, our health suffers.
      </p>
      <p>
        At <strong>Spicery Co.</strong>, we recognize this food intake crisis as one of the most pressing health challenges of our time. We believe it is time to break the cycle of processed convenience and return to real cooking.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-image-wrapper">
      <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dawp1fcci/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1784235733/pexels-roman-odintsov-5332489_htsza3.jpg" alt="Dining table with wholesome vegetables">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!,  Section 2: Reclaiming the Natural Taste , >
<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container about-grid reverse">
    <div class="about-text-block">
      <h2>Reclaiming Pure, Natural Taste</h2>
      <p>
        Our response to this crisis is simple: a return to nature. We believe the kitchen should be a source of strength, health, and joy, not disease. That is why we commit to sourcing and curating <strong>100% natural, unadulterated spices</strong>. 
      </p>
      <p>
        Our goal is to bring back the original, traditional taste that has been lost in pre-packaged spice mixes. Every spice in our collection is freshly ground in small, controlled batches, preserving the essential aromatic oils and antioxidants that nature intended. 
      </p>
      <p>
        There are no artificial flow agents, no silicone dioxide, no fillers, and no artificial colors in our pantry. We are leading this charge, providing you with clean seasonings to make healthy, wholesome cooking taste spectacular.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-image-wrapper">
      <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dawp1fcci/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1784235731/pexels-seyhmuskino-31717561_lzdzqv.jpg" alt="Rich raw spices close up">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

